1. *Ista* noć je bila puna svetlosti. (The same night was full of light.)
2. Znam da *isti* problem imaš i ti. (I know you have the same problem too.)
3. *Iste* boje su nam dve haljine. (Our two dresses are the same color.)
4. Došla si u *isto* vreme kad i ja. (You came at the same time as me.)
5. Nismo imali *istu* sreću. (We didn't have the same luck.)